data.title: Ronald Ernest Paul, born on August 20, 1935, in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, is a notable American physician, author, and former politician....
data.meta_description:
14 likes, 0 comments - sfl_nepal on September 21, 2023: "Ronald Ernest Paul, born on August 20, 1935, in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, is a notable American physician, author, and former politician. He is best known for his libertarian and conservative political views. Paul served as a U.S. Representative for Texas on multiple occasions, primarily from 1976 to 2013. During his political career, he gained a reputation for advocating limited government, individual #liberty, and a non-interventionist foreign policy. His passionate following, often referred to as "Ron Paul Revolution," had a significant impact on libertarian and conservative movements in the United States. Dr. Paul has also authored several books, further promoting his #libertarian ideology.

 #sflnepal #sasfl #sfl".
